# Project Overview
This repository provides an **MCP server** that exposes **5eTools-style** D&D data to LLMs.

## Hard Rules
- Treat `./5etools-src` as **read-only** input.
- Prefer **2024 rules** when duplicates exist, unless explicitly asked for 2014.
- **Never** hallucinate rules text. If unsure: call a tool.
- Cite entities using URIs: `fiveet://entity/{kind}/{source}/{slug}`.

## What to do by default
- When asked about monsters/spells/items: `search_entities` → `get_entity` (markdown).
- When given 5eTools `entries` blobs: call `render_entries`.
- When given `{@tag ...}`: call `resolve_tag`.

